    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_598279163" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/598279163" />
    <a title="Shannon Dillman" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/18930763-shannon-dillman"><img alt="Shannon Dillman" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1366542533p2/18930763.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/598279163?book_show_action=true">Apr 23, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Shannon Dillman" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Shannon Dillman" href="/user/show/18930763-shannon-dillman">Shannon Dillman</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18930763-shannon-dillman?shelf=health">health</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer598279163" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16688257621488623582">Hard to put down. I&apos;m a seasoned home cook/blogger. I make my own pastas, cheeses and pretty much everything from scratch. I love reading his thoughts, and experiences. I wish I could take a day or two off of work to devour this straight through. I was lucky enough to get a signed book plate from him. :)</span>
  <span id="freeText16688257621488623582" style="display:none">Hard to put down. I'm a seasoned home cook/blogger. I make my own pastas, cheeses and pretty much everything from scratch. I love reading his thoughts, and experiences. I wish I could take a day or two off of work to devour this straight through. I was lucky enough to get a signed book plate from him. :)</span>
