<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/139220.Heat"><img alt="Heat: An Amateur&#39;s Adventures as Kitchen Slave, Line Cook, Pasta-Maker, and Apprentice to a Dante-Quoting Butcher in Tuscany" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1320554917l/139220._SX98_.jpg" />
