<span id="freeTextContainer12902372190036458163"><b>Michael Pollan</b> is an American author, journalist, activist, and professor of journalism at the University of California, Berkeley, where he is also the director of the Knight Program in Science and Environmental Journalism.<br/><br/><i>Excerpted from <a href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Pollan' rel='nofollow noopener'>Wikipedia</a>.</i></span>
